React Props & Components

Today's Focus: Props, Reusable Components, Children Prop
What I Learned: How to pass data between components. Learned:

Props as function parameters

Default props

PropTypes for type checking

Destructuring props

Children prop for nested content

Component composition

Practice Example: Card Component
function Card({ title, description, children }) {
    return (
        <div className="card">
            <h3>{title}</h3>
            <p>{description}</p>
            {children}
        </div>
    );
}

// Usage
<Card title="React Props" description="Learning props today">
    <button>Learn More</button>
</Card>
